Usage: read_parallel_edit_files [-help] [-check]
                                [-conflict_mode {only_one stop_all}]
                                -files <string> [-ignore_error]
                                [-report_file <string>]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
-check                                 # Specifies only check the syntax and
                                       # conflict of the files (bool, optional)
-conflict_mode {only_one stop_all}     # Specifies the conflict mode
                                       # (enum, optional)
-files <string>                        # Specifies the list of reading file
                                       # (string, required)
-ignore_error                          # Specifies whether ignore the errors in
                                       # files (bool, optional)
-report_file <string>                  # Specifies the name of conflict report
                                       # (string, optional)